// Slider
// Range slider with a filled track gradient showing the current position.

FUNCTION handleChange(e)
  Parses the slider value.
  Updates internal state and calls onChange with the new numeric value.

---

FUNCTION Slider(props) -> ReactNode                                       EXPORT
  Renders an HTML range input with a CSS gradient fill showing progress from min to current value.
  Displays the current value next to the slider.
